1
00:00:43,613 --> 00:00:47,842
=Live or Love?=

2
00:00:48,832 --> 00:00:52,256
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:56,992 --> 00:00:58,632
Before, she'd rather escape the wedding.

4
00:00:59,272 --> 00:01:00,111
Now she claims

5
00:01:00,111 --> 00:01:02,032
she is Yushen's wife and wants to help.

6
00:01:02,431 --> 00:01:03,751
Can Fang Lili

7
00:01:04,111 --> 00:01:05,111
be trusted?

8
00:01:05,312 --> 00:01:06,631
It has only been three days.

9
00:01:07,111 --> 00:01:08,751
How has she changed so quickly?

10
00:01:10,271 --> 00:01:10,751
Yushen,

11
00:01:11,232 --> 00:01:12,152
listen to me.

12
00:01:12,631 --> 00:01:13,631
For this kind of woman,

13
00:01:14,312 --> 00:01:15,872
you should stay away from her.

14
00:01:16,191 --> 00:01:16,831
Grandma,

15
00:01:16,911 --> 00:01:17,351
Dad,

16
00:01:18,312 --> 00:01:19,631
I have a few words to say.

17
00:01:20,032 --> 00:01:20,712
Go ahead.

18
00:01:21,831 --> 00:01:23,471
In fact, I always have feelings for her.

19
00:01:25,751 --> 00:01:26,592
A person

20
00:01:26,872 --> 00:01:28,032
follows her own heart,

21
00:01:28,351 --> 00:01:29,432
no matter how others think.

22
00:01:29,592 --> 00:01:30,432
This is not wrong.

23
00:01:30,751 --> 00:01:31,872
On the contrary, I feel

24
00:01:32,471 --> 00:01:34,271
such a person is more deserving of love.

25
00:01:34,872 --> 00:01:36,271
You call this

26
00:01:36,631 --> 00:01:37,991
following her heart?

27
00:01:38,152 --> 00:01:39,991
If Lili were an ordinary girl,

28
00:01:40,032 --> 00:01:41,191
for someone she likes,

29
00:01:41,271 --> 00:01:42,872
she would make breakfast, take the bus.

30
00:01:43,032 --> 00:01:44,111
This sounds

31
00:01:44,432 --> 00:01:45,471
probably more touching.

32
00:01:45,592 --> 00:01:47,191
But unfortunately, she's too rich.

33
00:01:47,631 --> 00:01:48,991
When she treats someone well,

34
00:01:49,351 --> 00:01:50,991
she just spends money on them.

35
00:01:51,111 --> 00:01:52,351
Is that her fault?

36
00:01:52,551 --> 00:01:54,032
She just gives her all.

37
00:01:54,432 --> 00:01:56,471
Why should we look down on her for that?

38
00:02:00,191 --> 00:02:00,831
Grandma,

39
00:02:01,351 --> 00:02:02,152
Lili

40
00:02:02,351 --> 00:02:03,751
was into Luo Yan before.

41
00:02:04,032 --> 00:02:05,152
I had no comment.

42
00:02:05,432 --> 00:02:07,152
But now she has chosen me.

43
00:02:07,872 --> 00:02:09,751
I don't want to miss her.

44
00:02:10,112 --> 00:02:11,872
I have no time to listen to you ranting.

45
00:02:12,592 --> 00:02:13,992
If she's willing to help you,

46
00:02:13,992 --> 00:02:14,992
that's her business.

47
00:02:15,832 --> 00:02:16,592
About this,

48
00:02:17,552 --> 00:02:18,992
don't come asking my advice anymore.

49
00:02:23,032 --> 00:02:23,712
Grandma.

50
00:02:30,432 --> 00:02:32,432
If she's willing pay for you, let her.

51
00:02:33,191 --> 00:02:35,152
You two aren't officially married.

52
00:02:35,751 --> 00:02:37,312
Let her stay in another room for now.

53
00:02:37,832 --> 00:02:38,592
Thank you, Grandma.

54
00:02:49,432 --> 00:02:50,392
(What's going on?)

55
00:02:50,791 --> 00:02:52,471
(Why should I care so much?)

56
00:02:53,152 --> 00:02:53,872
(If not for him,)

57
00:02:53,872 --> 00:02:55,312
(I might have gotten out already.)

58
00:02:57,552 --> 00:02:58,231
(Forget it.)

59
00:02:59,032 --> 00:03:00,671
(Consider it the game experience.)

60
00:03:00,992 --> 00:03:02,671
(I need to get him to sign it soon.)

61
00:03:02,872 --> 00:03:04,112
(I'll trap him just the same.)

62
00:03:11,592 --> 00:03:12,992
Sorry, I startled you.

63
00:03:14,152 --> 00:03:14,671
It's fine.

64
00:03:15,471 --> 00:03:16,552
How did the talk go?

65
00:03:17,671 --> 00:03:18,751
I guess they agreed.

66
00:03:19,791 --> 00:03:20,552
I'm sorry.

67
00:03:20,791 --> 00:03:22,351
It was me who borrowed money from you,

68
00:03:22,511 --> 00:03:23,552
yet you had to defend me.

69
00:03:24,631 --> 00:03:26,152
Your business is my business.

70
00:03:26,351 --> 00:03:27,552
We are friends, after all.

71
00:03:28,351 --> 00:03:29,671
So, can we sign the contract?

72
00:03:29,872 --> 00:03:30,351
Of course.

73
00:03:32,191 --> 00:03:33,432
But, Miss Fang,

74
00:03:33,951 --> 00:03:35,911
you said that you were mine.

75
00:03:37,112 --> 00:03:38,592
Were you serious about that?

76
00:03:39,751 --> 00:03:40,071
Ah?

77
00:03:42,351 --> 00:03:43,112
I knew it.

78
00:03:43,312 --> 00:03:44,231
You were simply kind.

79
00:03:45,231 --> 00:03:47,552
(What does his disappointed look mean?)

80
00:03:50,671 --> 00:03:51,552
Don't worry.

81
00:03:52,032 --> 00:03:53,671
Although Grandma let you move in,

82
00:03:53,791 --> 00:03:54,592
as soon as possible,

83
00:03:54,872 --> 00:03:55,992
I will still make it clear.

84
00:03:56,432 --> 00:03:56,872
Wait.

85
00:03:59,351 --> 00:04:00,471
Move into the An family?

86
00:04:03,152 --> 00:04:03,992
Miss Fang,

87
00:04:04,231 --> 00:04:05,751
lights are off. Rest early.

88
00:04:05,992 --> 00:04:07,671
Madam An asked me to relay the message.

89
00:04:07,671 --> 00:04:09,552
Yushen and you are not yet married.

90
00:04:09,671 --> 00:04:10,872
Please uphold the propriety.

91
00:04:17,551 --> 00:04:20,192
(Why do I feel like I've been duped?)

92
00:04:27,072 --> 00:04:28,111
Mr. Luo. We arrived.

93
00:04:30,832 --> 00:04:31,311
Mr. Luo?

94
00:04:38,832 --> 00:04:39,632
Why am I here?

95
00:04:40,072 --> 00:04:40,551
Mr. Luo,

96
00:04:40,712 --> 00:04:42,512
you called me to get you
from the An's place.

97
00:04:43,791 --> 00:04:44,991
From the An's place?

98
00:04:46,592 --> 00:04:47,592
When was that?

99
00:04:51,512 --> 00:04:52,871
Are you satisfied now?

100
00:04:53,911 --> 00:04:54,871
Our family affair

101
00:04:55,152 --> 00:04:56,871
is none of your business.

102
00:04:56,871 --> 00:04:57,871
Then, I'll be leaving.

103
00:04:58,072 --> 00:04:58,952
Please take care.

104
00:04:59,192 --> 00:04:59,952
Madam An.

105
00:05:00,512 --> 00:05:01,392
Why am I here?

106
00:05:01,752 --> 00:05:03,991
Mr. Luo, you called me to get you
from the An's place.

107
00:05:26,712 --> 00:05:27,632
Is Madam An asleep?

108
00:05:28,871 --> 00:05:30,072
She just went to bed.

109
00:05:30,072 --> 00:05:31,192
What about An Yushen's key?

110
00:05:31,192 --> 00:05:32,351
Has it been handed over?

111
00:05:35,431 --> 00:05:36,192
Yes, but

112
00:05:36,871 --> 00:05:38,272
Fang Lili

113
00:05:38,311 --> 00:05:39,632
covered his shortfall,

114
00:05:40,952 --> 00:05:41,952
so

115
00:05:42,632 --> 00:05:44,311
he can't leave Ju'an yet.

116
00:05:44,752 --> 00:05:45,632
Fang Lili?

117
00:05:46,512 --> 00:05:47,712
When did she go there?

118
00:05:48,431 --> 00:05:49,752
She came right after you left.

119
00:05:50,551 --> 00:05:51,712
Didn't you see her?

120
00:05:57,311 --> 00:05:58,512
Doesn't she hate An Yushen?

121
00:05:58,512 --> 00:05:59,072
Why?

122
00:06:00,311 --> 00:06:01,311
I don't know.

123
00:06:02,431 --> 00:06:03,192
What did Dad say?

124
00:06:05,072 --> 00:06:06,512
Madam An agreed.

125
00:06:07,351 --> 00:06:08,072
So,

126
00:06:08,871 --> 00:06:10,311
Mr. An had nothing to say.

127
00:06:13,991 --> 00:06:15,392
She, for An Yushen,

128
00:06:16,632 --> 00:06:17,952
can tolerate Fang Lili.

129
00:06:19,632 --> 00:06:21,192
Yet they can't let me join the family.

130
00:06:23,512 --> 00:06:24,871
Haven't had dinner yet, have you?

131
00:06:25,871 --> 00:06:26,871
I'll make you something.

132
00:06:36,192 --> 00:06:37,392
You're a member of the family.

133
00:06:37,632 --> 00:06:38,752
Sooner or later you will be.

134
00:07:18,752 --> 00:07:19,752
What are you thinking?

135
00:07:22,111 --> 00:07:23,471
As long as Madam An is around,

136
00:07:25,311 --> 00:07:27,592
I can't rightfully inherit Ju'an.

137
00:07:28,152 --> 00:07:29,192
And An Yushen will always

138
00:07:29,192 --> 00:07:31,111
bother me like a fly.

139
00:07:34,072 --> 00:07:36,111
Grandma has bought a house abroad.

140
00:07:37,832 --> 00:07:38,952
She should know

141
00:07:39,471 --> 00:07:41,192
An Yushen won't stay in Ju'an for long.

142
00:07:45,671 --> 00:07:46,791
Once An Yushen leaves,

143
00:07:47,712 --> 00:07:48,832
Ju'an will be yours.

144
00:07:50,592 --> 00:07:51,712
I'll always be with you.

145
00:07:53,272 --> 00:07:54,392
You should go back.

146
00:07:55,111 --> 00:07:56,752
Madam An may grow suspicious.

147
00:08:28,551 --> 00:08:29,512
Gran-Grandma?

148
00:08:30,871 --> 00:08:32,112
What are you doing here?

149
00:08:33,152 --> 00:08:33,992
What?

150
00:08:34,752 --> 00:08:36,352
Can't I come to your room?

151
00:08:37,112 --> 00:08:38,112
It's so late.

152
00:08:38,112 --> 00:08:39,112
Where have you been?

153
00:08:40,112 --> 00:08:40,632
I...

154
00:08:42,472 --> 00:08:44,352
I went to the office to get something.

155
00:09:00,392 --> 00:09:00,992
Lin Lu.

156
00:09:03,071 --> 00:09:04,752
You're newly graduated.

157
00:09:05,431 --> 00:09:08,112
Intern in the office of Ju'an's CEO

158
00:09:09,352 --> 00:09:11,112
is a rare opportunity.

159
00:09:12,512 --> 00:09:13,392
I know.

160
00:09:14,232 --> 00:09:15,911
Grandma, you helped me

161
00:09:16,392 --> 00:09:17,791
and care about me.

162
00:09:17,791 --> 00:09:18,872
I'll keep it in mind.

163
00:09:19,512 --> 00:09:21,272
Your parents had an accident.

164
00:09:22,352 --> 00:09:24,112
I adopted you,

165
00:09:25,112 --> 00:09:27,352
regarding you as a member of our family.

166
00:09:28,112 --> 00:09:30,551
This time, Li Zheng and the others
resigned together,

167
00:09:30,911 --> 00:09:31,992
why didn't you

168
00:09:32,392 --> 00:09:33,872
inform Yushen in advance?

169
00:09:37,911 --> 00:09:38,752
Grandma,

170
00:09:39,512 --> 00:09:40,711
my place is not high enough.

171
00:09:41,112 --> 00:09:43,352
There are many things I didn't know.

172
00:09:44,392 --> 00:09:45,992
If I had known,

173
00:09:46,392 --> 00:09:48,992
how could I not have told Yushen?

174
00:09:52,112 --> 00:09:52,911
Grandma,

175
00:09:53,632 --> 00:09:55,272
I know what I need to do.

176
00:09:57,711 --> 00:09:59,112
Everything I have today

177
00:09:59,512 --> 00:10:00,711
is given by you.

178
00:10:10,624 --> 00:10:11,776
(Ju'an Group)

179
00:10:19,992 --> 00:10:20,551
Please sit.

180
00:10:25,752 --> 00:10:26,392
Thank you.

181
00:10:31,352 --> 00:10:33,152
I've reviewed the biweekly trend charts,

182
00:10:33,591 --> 00:10:35,791
today is the best time to buy crude oil.

183
00:10:37,272 --> 00:10:39,992
(After this, you'll lose everything)

184
00:10:40,512 --> 00:10:41,632
But before that,

185
00:10:41,632 --> 00:10:42,551
sign the contract.

186
00:10:42,551 --> 00:10:43,352
No problem, right?

187
00:10:43,352 --> 00:10:43,791
Yes.

188
00:10:46,352 --> 00:10:48,352
My key was taken away by my dad.

189
00:10:48,352 --> 00:10:50,232
I have to fill out an application form

190
00:10:50,232 --> 00:10:51,512
to retrieve the key.

191
00:10:51,512 --> 00:10:52,512
What company key?

192
00:10:52,831 --> 00:10:54,591
The one used for account transactions.

193
00:10:54,632 --> 00:10:55,512
Luo Yan and I

194
00:10:55,512 --> 00:10:56,392
each have one.

195
00:10:57,112 --> 00:10:57,911
But

196
00:10:58,032 --> 00:10:59,512
if I can't get it back,

197
00:10:59,512 --> 00:11:01,112
the transaction cannot proceed.

198
00:11:01,112 --> 00:11:02,752
Is this at odds with contract signing?

199
00:11:03,112 --> 00:11:04,112
What is the date today?

200
00:11:04,992 --> 00:11:05,872
July 25th.

201
00:11:05,911 --> 00:11:06,632
Okay, thank you.

202
00:11:09,152 --> 00:11:10,752
(Is he pretending to be ignorant?)

203
00:11:11,191 --> 00:11:12,671
(Does he not want to sign?)

204
00:11:15,951 --> 00:11:16,512
Mr. An,

205
00:11:16,752 --> 00:11:18,992
I always thought you were
a person of integrity.

206
00:11:19,232 --> 00:11:20,112
If you don't sign,

207
00:11:20,112 --> 00:11:20,872
I'll withdraw.

208
00:11:20,872 --> 00:11:21,752
Do you understand?

209
00:11:24,232 --> 00:11:25,752
Are you signing or not?

210
00:11:31,512 --> 00:11:32,152
I...

211
00:11:32,872 --> 00:11:33,512
I'll sign.

212
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,835
(Loan Agreement)

213
00:11:38,232 --> 00:11:38,992
I'm sorry.

214
00:11:39,752 --> 00:11:40,232
I...

215
00:11:40,911 --> 00:11:41,992
I didn't do it on purpose.

216
00:11:42,472 --> 00:11:42,992
Well,

217
00:11:43,112 --> 00:11:44,992
I'll have Feng make another copy.

218
00:11:45,512 --> 00:11:46,752
You can go directly to him.

219
00:11:47,152 --> 00:11:47,791
I'll get key.

220
00:11:47,791 --> 00:11:48,872
I'm going to get the key.

221
00:11:49,632 --> 00:11:50,512
You do the contract.

222
00:11:51,791 --> 00:11:53,512
I should go.

223
00:11:54,752 --> 00:11:55,911
Ten minutes later,

224
00:11:56,352 --> 00:11:57,711
I want to see the contract.

225
00:12:04,472 --> 00:12:05,272
Who are you?

226
00:12:05,512 --> 00:12:06,032
Scheduled?

227
00:12:06,032 --> 00:12:07,112
How can you barge in?

228
00:12:08,591 --> 00:12:09,872
I am An Yushen's fiancée.

229
00:12:10,112 --> 00:12:11,112
(Contract)
I need his key.

230
00:12:12,512 --> 00:12:13,992
So you are

231
00:12:14,992 --> 00:12:15,911
that one.

232
00:12:17,191 --> 00:12:18,152
I've heard about you.

233
00:12:18,791 --> 00:12:19,591
So,

234
00:12:20,152 --> 00:12:21,632
can I go take it now?

235
00:12:22,112 --> 00:12:22,752
Miss Fang,

236
00:12:22,911 --> 00:12:23,872
per the rules,

237
00:12:23,872 --> 00:12:25,632
I need to check with Mr. An

238
00:12:25,791 --> 00:12:27,032
and then review your form.

239
00:12:27,272 --> 00:12:28,112
After all,

240
00:12:28,311 --> 00:12:29,752
the key of Ju'an

241
00:12:30,232 --> 00:12:32,272
can't simply be given to just anyone.

242
00:12:37,674 --> 00:12:38,465
(Mr. Luo)

243
00:12:42,272 --> 00:12:43,872
In order to avoid further problems,

244
00:12:44,071 --> 00:12:44,831
I think

245
00:12:45,272 --> 00:12:46,152
we should

246
00:12:46,152 --> 00:12:48,791
discuss future investment strategies.

247
00:12:49,152 --> 00:12:49,911
Client's call.

248
00:12:53,992 --> 00:12:54,632
Mr. An,

249
00:12:54,791 --> 00:12:55,711
please take a look.

250
00:13:02,632 --> 00:13:02,992
Hello?

251
00:13:03,591 --> 00:13:04,032
Hello,

252
00:13:04,152 --> 00:13:04,911
Mr. An?

253
00:13:06,551 --> 00:13:08,272
Young An wants the key back.

254
00:13:09,951 --> 00:13:10,711
Hold them back.

255
00:13:12,071 --> 00:13:12,671
Understood.

256
00:13:17,232 --> 00:13:18,392
Can it be arranged now?

257
00:13:19,632 --> 00:13:20,112
Yes.

258
00:13:22,992 --> 00:13:24,472
However, it's already twelve o'clock.

259
00:13:24,472 --> 00:13:25,711
It's time for a lunch break.

260
00:13:25,872 --> 00:13:26,752
Lunch break?

261
00:13:27,392 --> 00:13:29,152
The form will take you five minutes.

262
00:13:29,152 --> 00:13:30,872
Sign it and then it will be good to go.

263
00:13:33,392 --> 00:13:34,512
Miss Fang,

264
00:13:34,752 --> 00:13:35,791
you probably never worked

265
00:13:35,791 --> 00:13:37,112
in such a big company, right?

266
00:13:37,551 --> 00:13:40,032
We have hundreds of forms daily.

267
00:13:40,512 --> 00:13:41,272
I have to

268
00:13:41,752 --> 00:13:43,591
check them one by one.

269
00:13:43,632 --> 00:13:45,392
It's not yet your turn.

270
00:13:45,752 --> 00:13:48,232
Can't or won't you review it?

271
00:13:48,591 --> 00:13:49,911
Miss Fang,

272
00:13:49,911 --> 00:13:51,872
that was somewhat unfair, wasn't it?

273
00:13:52,512 --> 00:13:53,352
Why do I feel

274
00:13:53,472 --> 00:13:54,551
that you are

275
00:13:54,992 --> 00:13:56,992
lack of manners?

276
00:13:58,671 --> 00:13:59,272
I'm sorry,

277
00:13:59,272 --> 00:13:59,872
I forgot you've

278
00:14:00,112 --> 00:14:01,711
made your father die in anger.

279
00:14:06,872 --> 00:14:07,752
Sorry, Miss Fang.

280
00:14:07,752 --> 00:14:08,791
I have low blood sugar.

281
00:14:09,112 --> 00:14:10,472
I need to go and have lunch first.

282
00:14:20,232 --> 00:14:20,872
Sorry,

283
00:14:21,152 --> 00:14:22,272
I didn't mean it.

284
00:14:32,951 --> 00:14:33,752
Stop watching!

285
00:14:37,591 --> 00:14:40,472
I hate the roles play too many tricks.

286
00:14:46,431 --> 00:14:47,512
Your key.

287
00:14:50,152 --> 00:14:50,551
You...

288
00:14:50,671 --> 00:14:51,711
How did you get it?

289
00:14:51,831 --> 00:14:53,152
Hurry up and buy your crude oil.

290
00:14:53,504 --> 00:14:54,232
(Ju'an Group)

291
00:14:54,232 --> 00:14:55,112
Mr. An!

292
00:14:55,272 --> 00:14:56,112
Mr. An!

