you're finally getting it.

587
00:28:03,161 --> 00:28:05,831
(30th Anniversary Celebration)

588
00:28:05,831 --> 00:28:06,752
Don't be nervous.

589
00:28:08,591 --> 00:28:10,591
(He looks rather pleasing now.)

590
00:28:10,871 --> 00:28:12,032
(Once I get out,)

591
00:28:12,232 --> 00:28:13,871
(I'll definitely give you more parts.)

592
00:28:30,752 --> 00:28:32,791
I heard you've made
a fool of yourself again.

593
00:28:33,871 --> 00:28:35,232
Hasn't the Fang family taught you

594
00:28:35,232 --> 00:28:36,591
the meaning of shame?

595
00:28:37,232 --> 00:28:38,151
Show some dignity.

596
00:28:38,151 --> 00:28:39,351
Leave the An family.

597
00:28:39,791 --> 00:28:40,952
Don't make me say it again.

598
00:28:42,752 --> 00:28:43,831
Come back here.

599
00:28:44,551 --> 00:28:46,032
Who are you talking to?

600
00:28:46,591 --> 00:28:47,912
I'm about to go out right now.

601
00:28:47,912 --> 00:28:48,752
Time is limited,

602
00:28:48,912 --> 00:28:50,432
So I'll scold you for five minutes.

603
00:28:50,432 --> 00:28:51,311
Fang Lili.

604
00:28:51,432 --> 00:28:51,871
You...

605
00:28:58,192 --> 00:28:59,151
An Xiangyang, right?

606
00:28:59,752 --> 00:29:00,952
Who named you?

607
00:29:00,952 --> 00:29:02,032
Such an awful name.

608
00:29:02,311 --> 00:29:03,631
Although you're not human,

609
00:29:03,631 --> 00:29:05,551
I still aim to teach you some
human principles.

610
00:29:05,631 --> 00:29:07,551
Man acts, Heaven watches.

611
00:29:07,831 --> 00:29:10,512
A character like you will
not meet a good end.

612
00:29:10,512 --> 00:29:11,272
Fang Lili,

613
00:29:11,752 --> 00:29:13,992
I will make you pay for these words.

614
00:29:14,071 --> 00:29:14,712
Sorry.

615
00:29:15,111 --> 00:29:16,472
I'll be out in a minute.

616
00:29:16,752 --> 00:29:17,752
You have no chance.

617
00:29:17,752 --> 00:29:18,631
Hello everyone.

618
00:29:19,151 --> 00:29:20,192
Thank you all

619
00:29:20,672 --> 00:29:22,912
for attending
the appreciation banquet of Ju'an Group.

620
00:29:23,071 --> 00:29:24,551
I want to take this opportunity

621
00:29:24,791 --> 00:29:25,952
to announce something.

622
00:29:26,232 --> 00:29:27,232
Over the years,

623
00:29:27,432 --> 00:29:28,472
my power is limited,

624
00:29:28,992 --> 00:29:30,871
and have led to losses for the company.

625
00:29:31,672 --> 00:29:32,631
My father

626
00:29:32,631 --> 00:29:33,912
is advanced in years.

627
00:29:34,391 --> 00:29:35,831
And he has been choosing

628
00:29:35,831 --> 00:29:37,871
someone to lead Ju'an into the future.

629
00:29:38,071 --> 00:29:38,912
I know,

630
00:29:39,631 --> 00:29:40,591
perhaps Luo Yan

631
00:29:40,591 --> 00:29:43,192
is more suited to be CEO
of Ju'an Group than I am.

632
00:29:43,591 --> 00:29:45,272
But I still want to make an effort.

633
00:29:46,151 --> 00:29:47,192
For the one I love,

634
00:29:47,952 --> 00:29:49,192
those who have helped me,

635
00:29:49,192 --> 00:29:50,512
and for myself as well,

636
00:29:53,192 --> 00:29:54,672
I believe that I can lead Ju'an

637
00:29:54,952 --> 00:29:55,831
towards the future.

638
00:29:57,082 --> 00:29:59,168
♪How could you see through
what's in my mind♪

639
00:29:59,168 --> 00:30:02,531
♪This moment, don't hold hands anymore♪

640
00:30:03,584 --> 00:30:06,442
♪Could it be that
you control my true love♪

641
00:30:07,791 --> 00:30:09,432
Congrats on finishing the first task.

642
00:30:09,432 --> 00:30:10,672
You've made an improvement,

643
00:30:10,672 --> 00:30:11,551
reward of

644
00:30:11,551 --> 00:30:12,672
three hundred coins.

645
00:30:13,071 --> 00:30:13,952
An Hang,

646
00:30:13,952 --> 00:30:15,071
please put on the helmet,

647
00:30:15,071 --> 00:30:15,992
wait for it to load.

648
00:30:15,992 --> 00:30:16,791
Your consciousness

649
00:30:16,791 --> 00:30:17,831
will enter the game.

650
00:30:18,464 --> 00:30:21,992
♪Every minute is still wonderful♪

651
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,752
♪No need for sentiments
beyond affection♪

652
00:30:24,752 --> 00:30:26,752
Welcome to Live or Love?

653
00:30:26,992 --> 00:30:28,871
Your character is An Yushen,

654
00:30:28,952 --> 00:30:30,232
mission is to defeat Luo Yan

655
00:30:30,232 --> 00:30:32,111
and become CEO of Ju'an Group.

656
00:30:32,432 --> 00:30:34,512
I am your exclusive game butler,

657
00:30:34,512 --> 00:30:35,432
Aotian.

658
00:30:35,432 --> 00:30:36,192
(Live or Love?)

659
00:30:36,992 --> 00:30:37,672
Aotian.

660
00:30:37,912 --> 00:30:38,432
I'm here.

661
00:30:38,752 --> 00:30:40,111
Are you sure that Fang Lili has

662
00:30:40,311 --> 00:30:41,752
fifty million in assets?

663
00:30:43,952 --> 00:30:44,591
Luo Yan, listen.

664
00:30:44,591 --> 00:30:45,672
I can help you.

665
00:30:52,391 --> 00:30:53,512
What do you mean?

666
00:30:53,512 --> 00:30:55,272
Wearing a wedding dress
without a wallet?

667
00:30:55,272 --> 00:30:56,111
Got dumped?

668
00:30:56,111 --> 00:30:57,432
Here to take revenge on society?

669
00:30:58,992 --> 00:30:59,912
Use my card.

670
00:31:00,351 --> 00:31:00,912
Yeah.

671
00:31:01,712 --> 00:31:02,631
Crude oil

672
00:31:02,791 --> 00:31:03,551
lost money,

673
00:31:04,272 --> 00:31:05,391
fifty million.

674
00:31:06,591 --> 00:31:07,952
I'm sorry, Grandma.

675
00:31:08,992 --> 00:31:10,311
I've let you down again.

676
00:31:11,840 --> 00:31:15,590
♪Waking up in the night rain,
crossing the nebula♪

677
00:31:15,590 --> 00:31:19,808
♪In the long night's breeze,
now I sing alone♪

678
00:31:19,808 --> 00:31:23,488
♪Fallen asleep,
wake up to a gentle dream♪

679
00:31:24,409 --> 00:31:27,879
♪Miss the past, can be reborn again♪

680
00:31:30,311 --> 00:31:32,791
I hope you can give me this opportunity

681
00:31:33,111 --> 00:31:36,151
and supervise me to continue growing.

682
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:09,142
♪I forgot the time and my promises♪

683
00:32:11,203 --> 00:32:16,032
♪How far I've gone,
