684
00:32:18,432 --> 00:32:23,232
♪In dreams, I still feel sorry for you♪

685
00:32:25,472 --> 00:32:30,479
♪I can't help missing you♪

686
00:32:31,488 --> 00:32:36,032
♪My life got dull without you♪

687
00:32:36,032 --> 00:32:39,417
♪I want to snuggle in your tenderness♪

688
00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:45,326
♪I mistakenly think that my stubbornness
can win back everything.♪

689
00:32:45,856 --> 00:32:50,106
♪I don't dare to reminisce♪

690
00:32:50,106 --> 00:32:53,759
♪For fear that tears fill my eyes♪

691
00:32:54,112 --> 00:32:57,659
♪I can't return to the past
and embrace you♪

692
00:32:57,965 --> 00:33:00,160
♪It's already in vain♪

693
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:03,712
♪I stood alone under the street light♪

694
00:33:03,712 --> 00:33:08,301
♪I can't find the courage to love♪

695
00:33:08,301 --> 00:33:09,728
♪I hope♪

696
